    &lt;span id=&quot;1-1&quot;&gt;1.1&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span id=&quot;1-2&quot;&gt;1.2&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span id=&quot;2-1&quot;&gt;2.1&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span id=&quot;2-2&quot;&gt;2.2&lt;/span&gt;


&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

You have at your disposition other ones too: **Contains** `*=` and  **Ends With** `$=` and more. Find out here [MDN - Attribute selectors][1]


